<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chawian un Lal Krista I Lalpen!
 Kumsawt in A chawiat la gi hen!
 Lopina, zahna A min piei tiu,
 Tu leh kumsawt chan in.

[V2]
 Chawian hitiu, chawian hitiu,
 Gam lopi ah Lalpen chawian ding;
 Chawian un, chawian un,
 A pahchak la sau un.

[V3]
 2. Chawian un, van sang a Angelte'n,
 A Lalchutphah gihawih in awi un;
 Namtin in chawihatna la sau hen,
 &quot;Lalte Lal chawian un.&quot;

[V4]
 3. Galhat ahi, gitlohna A zo,
 A thu'n I lunggil ah vaihawm hen;
 A min ziekin guolzawhna mu'i tiu,
 Kumsawtin chawian un.</lyrics>
<title>CROWN HIM KING!</title>
<hymn_number>35</hymn_number>
</song>